{"tid":246040,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲教徒評論黃毓民語錄一覧","createTime":"2017-05-16T16:34:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T17:51:26.000Z","uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d553f7b7dc6c6f3a7892569f5238e4a8a66f5188","tid":246040,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"Chiu Bryant 黃毓民落地獄<br />\n<br />\nSara Dylan 老師，某人已不惜𢱑爛自己塊面來抹黑你、羞辱你了，可惜力度不過如此<br />\n<br />\nKarlaen Chan 老師, 這種侮辱, 你無所謂, 我有所謂! 佢侮辱左投票比熱普誠的選民!!😡<br />\n<br />\nShirley Chiu 我投比黃毓民的一票是投比新界東的陳雲，當日我真的充滿希望老師可以當選，實現他的政綱!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155220598987225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155220598987225&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=efdaa239\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155220598987225</a><br />\n<br />\nKiis Prince 國師畀面佢，但佢無畀個幾分情面。<br />\n佢鍾意埋啲小人，唔怪得成日被人出賣。<br />\n<br />\n黃葉飛 黃毓民在網台節目中的言論, 是要將老師講成一個偽君子! (唔好以為所有人都係盲都係聾嘅)<br />\n<br />\nSiulok Chan 熟知狗主性格,一早估到後著,老師有劉備之志,圖忍辱負重,奈何遇到卑鄙小人,但焉知非福!!<br />\n<br />\nJones Chan 要講對唔住嗰個唔係你向我講，係MyRadio班撚屌同你講。<br />\nBTW 我以後同MyRadio/普羅冇任何關係。<br />\n<br />\nRock Wong 本來稱得上一號人物，而家聽信小人自貶身價變成當日出賣佢既鼠輩之流，可悲可笑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155217917032225?pnref=story\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155217917032225%3Fpnref%3Dstory&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b4f68fe3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155217917032225?pnref=story</a>"},{"pid":"f6e48cfea21ccc04ed600af399ece1d859a6081b","tid":246040,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"我投比黃毓民的一票是投比新界東的陳雲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{